{"tid":1468754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我想同大家講：其實從來都冇封曬所有入禁區嘅路，好大條走火通道比人入禁區，職員暗地都係咁帶人入去。","createTime":"2019-08-13T20:35:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T04:55:19.000Z","uid":29132,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d1d672a98d43b39b6a1ee935ce13d56a5436ead3","tid":1468754,"uid":29132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:35:37.000Z","msg":"我今日一直都係機場，其實機場入面好多示威者都知，反而連登冇咩人講。從來，從來，從來都冇封曬所有入禁區嘅路，好大條走火通道比人入禁區，職員暗地都係咁帶人入去。<br />\n<br />\n我只係想確保所有都知。"},{"pid":"e51a3e174dcff1094992deea72b819db9b20140e","tid":1468754,"uid":29132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:38:00.000Z","msg":"又或者叫內部通道，平時用嚟做員工通道個啲野啦，我唔肯定正確名稱。"},{"pid":"44bb927edf2838ead8e7035073310adf33fa6ecd","tid":1468754,"uid":29132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:38:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b19bbbb9d79d48cb02b482eee15d3425e5f9b342","tid":1468754,"uid":29132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:38:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"adabb756cf6797cf8e135e71ff196b0c20e8ca34","tid":1468754,"uid":272892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:40:33.000Z","msg":"總之香港人加油！永不放棄！"},{"pid":"0b5ed762ee6b07fc4e4be83d9a9032ce7817d7f0","tid":1468754,"uid":29132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:41:33.000Z","msg":"機場廣播指示遊客搵職員，當遊客搵職員就會帶佢地行走火通道入禁區。"},{"pid":"58ec4b7117172e7c5c28ff54e9ee9eacead0e30b","tid":1468754,"uid":29132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:42:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"81dc028ae16f40fb1ead3aa31c71c30e840dd45f","tid":1468754,"uid":29132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:42:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a96085f04c0405de0090310d186c98ebad6618b3","tid":1468754,"uid":29132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:42:57.000Z","msg":"大家都需要知真相"},{"pid":"1cdca886f272312ddc07efd8a2b9b79c3cf9a6d8","